Text-Affixes version 0.02
==========================

Text::Affixes - Basis for Prefixes and Sufixes analisys of text

=head1 SYNOPSIS

  use Text::Affixes;
  my $text = "Hello, world. Hello, big world.";
  my $prefixes = get_prefixes($text);

  # $prefixes now holds
  # {
  # 	3 => {
  # 		'Hel' => 2,
  # 		'wor' => 2,
  # 	}
  # }

  # or

  $prefixes = get_prefixes({min => 1, max => 2},$text);

  # $prefixes now holds
  # {
  # 	1 => {
  # 		'H' => 2,
  # 		'w' => 2,
  # 		'b' => 1,
  # 	},
  # 	2 => {
  # 		'He' => 2,
  # 		'wo' => 2,
  # 		'bi' => 1,
  # 	}
  # }

  # the use for get_sufixes is similar

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This module, still in its early stages, is meant to be used
in Natural Language Processing tools that require Prefixe or
Sufixe examination of text.

